URL: https://www2.swift.com/mystandards/#/mp/mx/_kijaUKEYEeuB-v2uhrZqSw/_qR07UZ5FEeyNX8SYmSuaLA
Description: FedNow Service Scope

The account reporting request is the message the FedNow participant uses to solicit a report from the FedNow Service.

FedNow Service Usage

The account reporting request is used to request the FedNow Service to send an account balance report, an account activity totals report, or an account activity details report.

If the account reporting request is successfully processed, then the FedNow Service will send the requested report to the FedNow participant using the ISO 20022 Bank-to-Customer Account Report message (camt.052).

